Class Extension

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Extension

  • public class Extension
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an auxiliary node in the XML tree to extend the Magic Draw specification Used to hold a DiagramRepresentation, a ModelExtension or a ReferenceExtension
